notesStmt.annot: Source MusicXML file created using Finale NotePad 2012 for Windows and Dolet Light for Finale NotePad 2012 on 2015-03-24.

normalization.p: Calculation of @tstamp and @tstamp2 values on control events, such as dir, dynam, hairpin, etc., includes MusicXML offset values.

The parameters for musicxml2mei.xsl were set as follows:
accidStyle: "attr",
articStyle: "elem",
formeWork: "strip",
generateMIDI: "false",
keepAttributes: "false",
keepRights: "true",
labelStyle: "attr",
layout: "strip",
tieStyle: "attr"

changeDesc.p: Transcoded from a MusicXML version 3.0 file using an XSLT stylesheet (musicxml2mei v. 3.0).
